":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2316959745","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2316959745","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjMxNjk1OTc0NQ==","status":"current","title":"TMP","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":887957284},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2316959745","tinyui":"/x/AQAaig","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2316959745","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2316959745/TMP","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2316959745"}},{"id":"2405957977","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2405957977","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjQwNTk1Nzk3Nw==","status":"current","title":"Auth Multiservices","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":612409765},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2405957977/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2405957977/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2405957977/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2405957977/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2405957977","tinyui":"/x/WQFojw","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2405957977","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2405957977/Auth+Multiservices","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2405957977"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<h1>Points to Consider</h1><ul><li><p>En la creaci&oacute;n de usuarios en el C4C, podr&iacute;a quedar mas de un usuario (IndividualAccount) creado con mismo email pero diferente user_id.</p></li><li><p>El  baas_token de auth se comparte entre servicios ya que solo se guarda en el redis identificado por el email del usuario. Actualmente esto ya genera conflicto cuando un usuario utiliza tanto la app de MPOS como la de Pago Movil. Este error se va a mantener con el cambio nuevo e incluso se podr&iacute;a agravar si se utiliza esa forma de autenticaci&oacute;n desde otros aplicativos.</p></li><li><p>Los mails de activaci&oacute;n y recuperaci&oacute;n de contrase&ntilde;a son gen&eacute;ricos y el usuario va a recibir exactamente el mismo mail si se registra de cualquier servicio de bancard. Algo a considerar es crear mails customizados por servicio o que indiquen a que servicio pertenece.</p></li></ul><h1>Points to Discuss</h1><ul><li><p>En billing-service se utiliza el endpoint get_user_by_email de auth. Habr&iacute;a que mandar el origin? Solo se usa para las operaciones <code>create_transfer_request</code> , <code>create_transfer_payment</code>.</p></li><li><p>En bportal hay que agregar el origin en los endpoints que corresponda.</p></li><li><p>En commerce-service se utiliza la operaci&oacute;n <code>get_users(q)</code> sin enviar el user_id, solo el email. Con los nuevos cambios podr&iacute;a darse que hayan mas de un usuario con el mismo email. Como resolvemos? Recibimos un parametro de origin opcional en la operaci&oacute;n <code>get_users</code> de auth? Enviamos desde commerce-service el service_code para filtrar?</p></li></ul><h1>Required Changes</h1><ul><li><p>Run migrations 29, 30, 31 and 32</p></li><li><p>Insert services on staging database</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"ba15d0d7-5f9d-4cea-b637-fb48103363ac\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"language\">sql</ac:parameter><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[INSERT INTO services (code, name, reset_password_url, reset_password_return_url)\nVALUES (0, \"General\", \"https://desa.infonet.com.py:8092/auth/users/reset-password?user_id=:user_id&reset_token=:reset_token\",\"https://desa.infonet.com.py:8035/sessions/new\")\n\nINSERT INTO services (code, name, reset_password_url, reset_password_return_url)\nVALUES (1, \"Pago Movil\", \"https://desa.infonet.com.py:8092/auth/users/reset-password?user_id=:user_id&reset_token=:reset_token\",\"https://desa.infonet.com.py/sessions/new\")\n\nINSERT INTO services (code, name, reset_password_url, reset_password_return_url)\nVALUES (2, \"General Sin Pago Movil\", \"https://desa.infonet.com.py:8092/auth/users/reset-password?user_id=:user_id&reset_token=:reset_token\",\"https://desa.infonet.com.py:8035/sessions/new\")\n\nINSERT INTO services (code, name, reset_password_url, reset_password_return_url)\nVALUES (6, \"TPago\", \"https://desa.infonet.com.py:8092/auth/users/reset-password?user_id=:user_id&reset_token=:reset_token\",\"https://temp.bancard.com.py:9443/sessions/new\")]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro></li><li><p>Insert services on production database</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"1e79c610-e3bb-467d-83e6-0ab03a2ead50\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"language\">sql</ac:parameter><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[INSERT INTO services (code, name, reset_password_url, reset_password_return_url)\nVALUES (0, \"General\", \"https://www.bancard.com.py/auth/users/reset-password?user_id=:user_id&reset_token=:reset_token\",\"https://comercios.bancard.com.py/sessions/new\")\n\nINSERT INTO services (code, name, reset_password_url, reset_password_return_url)\nVALUES (1, \"Pago Movil\", \"https://www.bancard.com.py/auth/users/reset-password?user_id=:user_id&reset_token=:reset_token\",\"https://www.infonet.com.py/sessions/new\")\n\nINSERT INTO services (code, name, reset_password_url, reset_password_return_url)\nVALUES (2, \"General Sin Pago Movil\", \"https://www.bancard.com.py/auth/users/reset-password?user_id=:user_id&reset_token=:reset_token\",\"https://comercios.bancard.com.py/sessions/new\")\n\nINSERT INTO services (code, name, reset_password_url, reset_password_return_url)\nVALUES (6, \"TPago\", \"https://www.bancard.com.py/auth/users/reset-password?user_id=:user_id&reset_token=:reset_token\",\"https://www.tpago.com.py/sessions/new\")]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro></li></ul><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2406285327"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":927},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2406285327/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2406285327/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2406285327/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2406285327/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2406285327","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2406285327/auth-service","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2406285327","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2406285327","tinyui":"/x/DwBtjw","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}